        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "*Disclosure: This post contains affiliate links. If you purchase through them, I may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you.*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have tried dozens of AI image generators over the past two years. Some are simple but limiting. Others are powerful but confusing. OpenArt AI hit the sweet spot: it gives you access to serious models like Stable Diffusion, FLUX, and ControlNet without requiring a computer science degree.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you have ever typed a prompt into an AI tool and gotten something mediocre back, this tutorial is for you. OpenArt AI changes that experience because it lets you control so much more of the creative process — and the results genuinely impress.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://openartai.pxf.io/c/6249333/3106413/38572"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start creating with OpenArt AI right now",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — it takes about two minutes to set up.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
