            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://openart.ai"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Head to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "openart.ai",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and create a free account. Once you are in, you will land on the OpenArt Suite — the central hub where all creation happens. The interface is clean: a left sidebar shows your options (Image, Video, Character, Audio, Story), and the main area is your workspace.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The free tier gives you credits to experiment, so you can start generating immediately without pulling out a credit card.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 2: Choose Your Model",
