          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "> *A red fox sitting on a mossy rock in a misty forest, digital painting, Studio Ghibli style, soft diffused lighting, highly detailed fur texture*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "OpenArt also offers a prompt enhancement feature. If your initial idea feels vague, click the enhance button and the platform will expand your prompt with relevant artistic descriptors.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/openart-ai-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Want to get better at prompting? Read our ",
