      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For your first few generations, keep the guidance scale around 7-9 and let the seed randomize. You will quickly see how small prompt changes create dramatically different results.",
