      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Edit",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — use the built-in editing suite to inpaint, outpaint, or modify specific areas",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This editing capability is a huge deal. You do not need to export to Photoshop. If the fox in your image has three tails instead of one (it happens), you can select that area and re-prompt just that section.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 6: Use ControlNet for Precise Control",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where OpenArt moves from \"fun tool\" to \"serious creative platform.\" ControlNet lets you upload a reference image — a pose sketch, a depth map, a line drawing — and the AI will follow that structure while applying your prompt's style.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For example: upload a stick figure in a specific pose, then prompt \"a samurai warrior in full armor, cinematic lighting.\" OpenArt will generate a fully rendered samurai in that exact pose.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This feature alone makes OpenArt worth the subscription for professional creators who need consistent compositions.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
